Class AbstractControlNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hpi.bpt.chimera.jcomparser.saving.AbstractControlNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractDataControlNode, EventBasedGateway, ExclusiveGateway, ParallelGateway

    public abstract class AbstractControlNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Possible control nodes are gateways, activities, webtasks and events. Each of them get saved in the ControlNode table and can be part of control flow.
